data.description: Charming two-story home with great curb appeal. Step inside from the spacious covered porch to an open floor plan complimented by spacious common areas with great natural light. Notable features include gorgeous luxury vinyl plank flooring, numerous windows, and crown molding. The formal dining is impressive with wainscot walls. The kitchen is the heart of the home with well-desired features including stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and tile backsplash. Spacious back yard with covered patio.
